    <label>pepsi frog</label>
    <description>This frog seems to be the product of some strange experiment by an ancient soda corporation truly rendered deranged by desperation. The milk of these frogs- yes, they produce milk, that's part of the genetics thing- is actually identical in texture and taste to the ancient drink known as 'pepsi'. It also comes in a can, for some reason.</description>
